         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-09/screenshot_2_3.jpg?VersionId=2S69w5ZUh.3Arylp5BJRl.af.JOermPd&amp;itok=HfWMGcgs" alt="" data-caption="据介绍，这艘长137米的潜艇上有12个导弹发射筒。（视频截取）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-09/screenshot_2_3.jpg?VersionId=2S69w5ZUh.3Arylp5BJRl.af.JOermPd&amp;itok=HfWMGcgs" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
